{"tid":513170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府擬向亞投行特別基金供款7800萬","createTime":"2017-12-29T09:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T14:25:18.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b769a946bce9194238b4ab76307ad6ecd85e25f","tid":513170,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:04:07.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府向立法會財委會申請撥款1000萬美元，即港幣約7800萬，向亞投行項目準備特別基金供款。<br />\n<br />\n政府向立法會提交的文件指，特別基金是支援及協助一些國家進行項目準備工作，早前就曾支援尼泊爾和斯里蘭卡的基礎設施項目。<br />\n<br />\n本港於今年3月獲財委會批准，分五年支付約12億元認購亞投行股本，正式成為亞投行成員。政府認為香港應和其他成員一同參與及支持亞投行的工作，以及展示援助中低收入成員的宗旨。"},{"pid":"9bad1c3951f43d6cc2930e3f9772902afa5af086","tid":513170,"uid":7369,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"又射7800萬落海，爽呀"},{"pid":"063ca5691bc20c46c6ff2c5caa979def4a0bfffd","tid":513170,"uid":75326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9bad1c3951f43d6cc2930e3f9772902afa5af086","tid":513170,"uid":7369,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"又射7800萬落海，爽呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:28:11.000Z","msg":"難為一帶一路先鋒何前局長去派利是，政府應該拎呢筆錢去拍戰狼3去救佢，不過唔知夠唔夠! 又要濕下水...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb86f8384a11c90436925b31cc3629f68c552dde","tid":513170,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又射7800萬落海，爽呀</blockquote><br />\n唔係比北京自己袋落袋咩"},{"pid":"063f531019c39c6ef905d5a68f0c0b814b2d1e21","tid":513170,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:23:39.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"29afd197c45d9315f46b0a37220de1f29bb05672","tid":513170,"uid":895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb86f8384a11c90436925b31cc3629f68c552dde","tid":513170,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又射7800萬落海，爽呀</blockquote><br />\n唔係比北京自己袋落袋咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20